gov.nih.nlm.meme.client
Class MergeEngineClient

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.client.ClientAPI
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.client.MergeEngineClient
public class MergeEngineClient
extends ClientAPI

This client API is used to process generate, load, and process sets of merge facts. See ClientAPI for information on configuring properties required by this class. To use, just instantiate it, configure it, and then call processMergeSet(). 

   // Instantiate client
   MergeEngineClient client = new MergeEngineClient();

   // Process merge set
   // This operation requires three parameters
   // 1. A work id
   // 2. An authority
   // 3. A merge set name
   int work_id = 12345;
   Authority authority = new Authority.Default("MSH2002");
   String merge_set = "MSH2002-M1";
   String log = client.processMergeSet(work_id, authority, merge_set);

Author:
MEME Group
